divs: Sighting DetailsIt was a very clear night, with no clouds, and the stars looked very bright. So I went outside and took some random photographs of the sky to see if any of the pictures would come out. I Observed nothing, I saw no ufo, or lights, until I got the pictures on my computer and in about a dozen or so photos I caught a snake like ufo, that seemed to change shape and color some. The pictures are all from different angles but clearly show the craft shape and colors. A few stars made it in the picture, which makes a great marker for the ufo object. I went out again about 2 hours later and took more photographs, and sure enough when I got inside I have a bunch more images of the object. I have the original images on my camera still, I also have all the original pictures on 2 computers. I have over a dozen images of this object. I am only releasing one photo of the object at this time.

Summary: After taking pictures of the stars, I found a ufo in the photos when I got them on my computer
